<br>
1. bladestorms are mezzable by rapture ( 50 mezz).  Mana intensive, but if you have 2 level 50+ enchanters you can just pull Djorn and have your enchanters mezz the bladestorms till your done.<br>
<br>
2.  Horsie splits are mezzable by dazzle or rapture.  Better to go with rapture as it is guarenteed mezz.  This isle becomes extremely simple as you just have your 59 + enchanter mezz one of the first splits, and your raid deals with the other.<br>
<br>
3. Vanquishers on spirocs are mezzable by rapture.<br>
<br>
4. Bzzzazzzt Bees are Dictatable, so you can dictate one of the main bees to help with the other fight.  You can dictate the bees ( charm ) for 48 seconds, then rapture then while your raid deals with the first bee.  This adds a LOT of damage, and relatively low risk to the raid since both dictate and rapture are basically irresistable on these mobs.<br>
<br>
This can turn bzzzazzt from hell to fairly easy, as long as proper timing is used. <p><a href="http://www.mithrilweb.com//"target="web"><img src="http://www.mithrilweb.com/images/sigs/llosig.jpg" border="0">

